Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.00,0:00:01.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,=========Pre=========
Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.00,0:00:01.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,=========OP=========
Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.22,0:00:05.73,oped,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}悲しみ連鎖の中で
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.92,0:00:15.37,oped,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}僕らの願いが届くまで…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.59,0:00:24.26,oped,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}大事なものまた一つ
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.18,0:00:28.88,oped,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}モノクロの空へと消える
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.34,0:00:35.67,oped,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}隠したキズ冷たく震え
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.11,0:00:40.05,oped,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}自分の居場所を探す
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.41,0:00:47.86,oped,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}常識に従うこの世界で
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.94,0:00:52.58,oped,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}どうしようもできないことを
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.43,0:00:56.78,oped,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}壊していきたくて
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.85,0:01:04.33,oped,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}閉ざしたココロ叫んでいる
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.22,0:01:11.78,oped,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}悲しみ連鎖の中で僕らは
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.88,0:01:17.42,oped,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}自分さえも見失いそうになって
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.10,0:01:21.35,oped,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}曖昧な答えはイラナイ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.45,0:01:27.86,oped,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,400)\be1}確かな今　追いかけて
Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.22,0:00:05.73,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}在悲傷的連鎖之中
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.92,0:00:15.37,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}在我們的願望實現之前
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.59,0:00:24.26,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}又一件珍貴的事物
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.18,0:00:28.88,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}消失在黑白的空中
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.34,0:00:35.67,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}隱藏的傷痕在發冷顫抖
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.11,0:00:40.05,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}去找尋我的容身之處吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.41,0:00:47.86,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}在這個遵循常識的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.94,0:00:52.58,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}想打破無可救藥的桎梏
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.43,0:00:56.78,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}按自己的意志自由生活
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.85,0:01:04.33,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}封閉的心靈正發出吶喊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.22,0:01:11.78,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}在悲傷的連鎖之中
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.88,0:01:17.42,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}我們幾乎快要迷失自我
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.10,0:01:21.35,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}不需要曖昧的答案
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.45,0:01:27.86,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,400)\be1}只需去追尋真切的現實
Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.00,0:00:01.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,=======TEXT=======
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.50,0:01:51.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾麗西婭
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.37,0:01:56.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,緊缺的醫用品也拜託了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.45,0:01:58.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 好的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.78,0:02:02.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…艾麗西婭
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.89,0:02:06.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剝奪進攻加利亞的指揮權？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.04,0:02:08.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這究竟…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.01,0:02:13.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,中央那群傢伙想讓我們停止進攻加利亞？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.86,0:02:16.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正是
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.64,0:02:18.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你必須明白 馬克西米利安
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.67,0:02:23.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我軍不能為攻略加利亞這樣的小國如此勞民傷財
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.77,0:02:29.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那歸根到底是為了在與聯邦軍的戰鬥中佔據優勢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.61,0:02:30.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.41,0:02:37.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們不得不提案解除你的指揮權
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.95,0:02:42.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恐不出一個月 議案就會被通過
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.75,0:02:44.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吾的指揮權難保
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.09,0:02:46.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.32,0:02:48.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒想到不是敵人
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.15,0:02:52.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反而是被自己人齊心合力趕出加利亞
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.61,0:02:53.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夠諷刺的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.01,0:02:56.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,並不意外
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.83,0:03:00.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,戰績不佳 還失去了格雷戈爾將軍
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.61,0:03:04.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吾難辭其咎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.98,0:03:07.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您打算怎麼辦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.65,0:03:11.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不想乖乖退居幕後吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.02,0:03:13.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當然
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.08,0:03:20.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然要祭出這玩意兒了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.59,0:03:32.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 OK了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.46,0:03:41.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是誰？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.57,0:03:43.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是第七小隊的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.81,0:03:46.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第…第一小隊的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.76,0:03:48.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在做什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.13,0:03:51.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剛結束日常維護
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.43,0:03:58.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這輛坦克不一般啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.79,0:04:01.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也開過許多坦克
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.72,0:04:05.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第一次見到保養得這麼好的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.91,0:04:07.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當然了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.91,0:04:09.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咋了？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.36,0:04:11.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼事？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.07,0:04:13.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剛才是誰？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.35,0:04:15.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第一小隊的年輕人
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.85,0:04:18.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟青春期小鬼似的沖頭沖腦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.16,0:04:20.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莫名其妙
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.21,0:04:24.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.97,0:04:34.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,隊長
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.07,0:04:36.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拉瑪爾 你在啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.07,0:04:39.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起 沒注意到
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.82,0:04:40.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒關係
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.84,0:04:42.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這種地方敬禮就免了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.82,0:04:47.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也在想心事沒發現 抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.45,0:04:51.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,隊長也會有心煩的事嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.14,0:04:55.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當然了 你當我是什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.08,0:04:55.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.39,0:04:58.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以為隊長和我這種人不同
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.44,0:05:02.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不會煩惱和消沉
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.11,0:05:06.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可不是超人
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.46,0:05:09.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,既會有煩惱 也會消沉的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.35,0:05:11.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和你區別不大
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.64,0:05:13.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.06,0:05:17.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 不過不會輕易消沉
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.16,0:05:23.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們的座右銘是「世上無難事 只怕有心人」
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.99,0:05:25.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.03,0:05:29.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是…是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.39,0:05:30.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,告辭
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.34,0:05:36.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也不能只顧著自己煩惱了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.11,0:05:46.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,馬克西米利安殿下
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.45,0:05:52.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我即便粉身碎骨也要重振殿下之雄風
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.43,0:05:55.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全隊 出發！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.95,0:06:12.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,耶格爾將軍
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.71,0:06:17.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,出動如此龐大的部隊 會被加利亞輕易發覺吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.94,0:06:19.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,目的正在於此
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.81,0:06:20.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.12,0:06:23.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,與加利亞開戰伊始
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.60,0:06:26.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們將戰線大舉推進到他們腹地
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.22,0:06:28.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但近來有被反攻的趨勢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.22,0:06:30.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為扭轉局面
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.65,0:06:35.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,發起總攻 擊垮他們主力是最便捷的手段
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.07,0:06:39.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為此 必須讓加利亞軍明白我們的動向
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.14,0:06:42.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,引他們主力出現
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.80,0:06:43.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原來如此
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.43,0:06:47.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過總攻也真是…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.57,0:06:50.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有必要這樣孤注一擲嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.58,0:06:52.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,做夢都沒想到
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.01,0:06:57.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他在軍隊中的地位如此搖搖欲墜了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.21,0:07:00.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,情勢緊迫
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.28,0:07:05.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,據報 帝國軍正在納齊亞平原集結
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.84,0:07:09.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幾乎調集了進攻加利亞的所有兵力
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.12,0:07:12.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,更引人注目的是
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.35,0:07:16.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,准皇太子馬克西米利安親自上陣指揮
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.72,0:07:19.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即是說 想對我們發起總攻嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.12,0:07:22.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他們終於也動真格的了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.79,0:07:24.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒事吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.85,0:07:29.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 不過也可以這樣理解吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.73,0:07:34.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他們被逼到必須決一死戰的地步了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.57,0:07:36.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被逼？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.75,0:07:39.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最近幾場戰鬥對他們而言可謂乏善可陳
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.49,0:07:43.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不僅如此 戰線還在被逐漸壓回
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.68,0:07:46.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們佔據了上風
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.50,0:07:50.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以帝國軍急於挽回頹勢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.84,0:07:53.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才會選擇此時發起總攻吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.02,0:07:58.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他們一定想借此扭轉戰局
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.07,0:08:00.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.41,0:08:01.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然不能輕敵
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.29,0:08:06.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但正如鞏特爾少尉所言 我們正佔據上風
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.86,0:08:08.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不必過分恐慌
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.49,0:08:10.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.03,0:08:13.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,無往不勝的第七小隊都這麼說
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.80,0:08:16.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們也還能打
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.57,0:08:22.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,隊長 請下令
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.30,0:08:25.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,煩惱解決了？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.20,0:08:27.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼 拉瑪爾
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.54,0:08:29.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有啥煩惱說來聽聽
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.01,0:08:31.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太見外了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.53,0:08:33.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼不告訴我們
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.42,0:08:35.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家是戰友 給點信任吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.84,0:08:37.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,隊長…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.82,0:08:39.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉 抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.16,0:08:43.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過和之前相比 似乎振作一點了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.00,0:08:47.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯 維爾金說得對
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.23,0:08:48.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,風正吹向我們
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.47,0:08:52.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們沒有解決不了的難題
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.31,0:08:54.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算沒有艾麗西婭的…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.93,0:08:56.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,…女武神的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.41,0:09:04.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 看來已經做好心理準備
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.63,0:09:06.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,決戰的時候到了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.56,0:09:08.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,準備出擊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.90,0:09:09.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,噢！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.48,0:09:20.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,科迪莉亞公主！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.66,0:09:23.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您要去哪兒？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.56,0:09:28.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,據聞加利亞軍將在納齊亞與帝國決戰
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.04,0:09:31.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我這就奔赴前線
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.39,0:09:33.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,萬萬不可
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.13,0:09:36.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去了又能如何？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.74,0:09:37.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知道…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.72,0:09:39.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即便如此
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.78,0:09:46.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即便如此 肯定有我力所能及的事
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.91,0:09:51.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果我的到場 能為將士們增添勇氣
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.25,0:09:54.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我義不容辭
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.12,0:10:08.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,納齊亞的戰鬥已經打響
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.02,0:10:11.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,作為左右戰局的一役
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.70,0:10:14.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,加利亞與帝國軍展開激烈的攻防
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.27,0:10:18.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以法爾迪奧的第一小隊為首
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.33,0:10:23.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,義勇軍的半數小隊在最前線與正規軍張起協同陣線
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.25,0:10:27.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,包括我們第七小隊在內的其他小隊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.69,0:10:31.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,則負責後方支援與掩護
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.69,0:10:36.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不論帕羅特上尉如何爭取
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.76,0:10:39.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第七小隊似乎並不受達蒙將軍的賞識
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.38,0:10:42.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們終日在營帳中度過
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.72,0:10:45.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,眼睜睜看著前線將士流血犧牲
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.61,0:10:53.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是啥？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.56,0:11:00.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,挺有兩下子的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.66,0:11:03.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,馬克西米利安還真是身先士卒啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.52,0:11:07.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那台Gerbil的戰速雖略低於歷來坦克
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.10,0:11:12.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其裝甲的厚度和攻擊破壞力異乎尋常
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.14,0:11:15.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓我們看看敵人會如何應對
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.63,0:11:16.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,發射
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.17,0:11:23.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打得漂亮 滋味如何 帝國的大笨象
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.59,0:11:29.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼會有這種坦克
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.02,0:11:34.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,報告 在敵人大型坦克的攻擊下
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.11,0:11:37.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正規軍第二小隊全滅
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.21,0:11:38.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,隊長 請指示
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.76,0:11:39.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別急 拉瑪爾
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.90,0:11:45.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,應該會有辦法
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.24,0:11:51.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,散熱器
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.21,0:11:54.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要看準它外露的瞬間
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.68,0:11:55.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,隊長…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.89,0:11:57.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別擔心
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.80,0:12:00.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不會讓你們去送死
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.75,0:12:03.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也別蠻幹
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.06,0:12:08.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 讓義勇軍部隊到這裡集結
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.07,0:12:11.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敵人必然會調頭追來
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.10,0:12:15.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,先把它引到這裡 行動起來
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.19,0:12:23.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了 艾麗西婭
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.70,0:12:25.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,維爾金
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.87,0:12:30.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白你很擔心 我們先做好份內事
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.70,0:12:31.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.54,0:12:38.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.17,0:12:42.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,將士們 我們是無所畏懼的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.40,0:12:46.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們堅定的意志將感動上蒼
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.99,0:12:52.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,加利亞公國世代傳承的女武神之矛與神盾在此
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.50,0:12:56.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,它們會保佑將士們擊退貪得無厭的帝國軍…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.58,0:12:59.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 保佑我們所有人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.19,0:13:06.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,效果雖然毋庸置疑 但是公主親臨前線
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.44,0:13:10.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果發生意外 也不想想是誰承擔責任
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.72,0:13:15.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是 科迪莉亞公主被稱為女武神族人的後裔
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.42,0:13:18.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那對長矛與神盾也是明證
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.11,0:13:20.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,女武神族？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.41,0:13:22.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那不過是民間傳說罷了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.20,0:13:34.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知為何 感覺加利亞軍的反擊勢頭更猛烈了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.08,0:13:36.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.35,0:13:40.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓馬克西米利安殿下的Gerbil後撤為好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.87,0:13:42.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,先不急
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.22,0:13:50.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看準它主炮發射後的瞬間
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.87,0:13:53.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,集中火力攻擊外露的散熱器
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.11,0:13:54.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.22,0:14:10.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就現在
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.37,0:14:19.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,停下了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.62,0:14:21.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 有戲
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.40,0:14:31.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不會錯 風…風正吹向我們
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.37,0:14:34.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好久不見
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.76,0:14:37.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 久違了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.66,0:14:39.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,士兵們在科迪莉亞公主的鼓舞下
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.07,0:14:42.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正開始發動反擊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.00,0:14:44.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感謝您不顧危險親赴戰地
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.63,0:14:48.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 危險與否不是問題
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.08,0:14:53.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是為加利亞盡自己的一份責任而已
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.64,0:14:59.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,馬克西米利安殿下的Gerbil被…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.25,0:15:03.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對方也鬥志旺盛啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.92,0:15:13.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.58,0:15:30.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.97,0:15:41.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,出現了 女武神
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.01,0:15:43.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惡
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.70,0:15:54.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別怯陣 開火！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.17,0:16:04.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是…什麼東西
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.43,0:16:06.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怪物嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.17,0:16:11.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,馬克西米利安殿下 下面請交給我
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.92,0:16:16.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,報告 前線正與疑似女武神人交戰
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.20,0:16:17.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.37,0:16:18.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,女武神人？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.68,0:16:22.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有信心嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.04,0:16:27.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.18,0:16:32.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.43,0:16:35.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,向它的正面集中火力
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.77,0:16:44.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算女武神族人
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.24,0:16:45.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也是血肉之軀
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.58,0:16:49.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,先逼她把盾牌固定在正面
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.30,0:16:52.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要求其他小隊掩護射擊 不要間斷
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.80,0:16:53.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.59,0:16:54.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,二班 三班
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.04,0:16:56.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,繞到她背後
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.67,0:16:58.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別和坦克糾纏
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.51,0:17:00.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,專心對付女武神
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.50,0:17:01.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.02,0:17:08.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 攻擊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.32,0:17:09.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自作聰明
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.40,0:17:17.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,隊長
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.88,0:18:36.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,找到了 是倖存者
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.66,0:18:51.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他就是唯一的倖存者嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.96,0:18:56.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,法爾迪奧 沒事吧 傷勢嚴重嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.79,0:18:58.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,法爾迪奧？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.75,0:19:02.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,發生什麼事
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.04,0:19:04.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快說明情況
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.66,0:19:09.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,稍等 他的狀態還無法回答問題
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.32,0:19:13.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請等他恢復
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.22,0:19:24.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這就是戰爭
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.04,0:19:29.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道 不可避免…雖然不可避免
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.11,0:19:32.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那種破壞力太不尋常
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.76,0:19:35.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,算是帝國軍的最新武器嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.40,0:19:39.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,報告 帝國的女武神正朝這裡逼近
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.26,0:20:02.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有信心
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.34,0:20:07.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,隊長
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.74,0:20:14.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,法爾迪奧？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.04,0:20:26.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是受傷了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.83,0:20:29.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要好好躺在醫務室休息才行
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.02,0:20:35.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾麗西婭…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.32,0:20:43.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒事…也不可能吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.52,0:20:45.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瞧我在說什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.84,0:20:56.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.64,0:21:01.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,需要幫忙儘管說
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.61,0:21:26.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾麗西婭 對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.00,0:00:01.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,=======ED=======
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.07,0:21:47.31,oped,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,400)\be1}悲しすぎる瞳が
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.77,0:21:53.98,oped,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,400)\be1}この空を映す
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.35,0:22:02.37,oped,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,400)\be1}掛ける言葉がわからずに
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.65,0:22:08.22,oped,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,400)\be1}ただ　星を数えた
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.74,0:22:13.94,oped,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,400)\be1}孤独で居る世界は
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.32,0:22:20.72,oped,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,400)\be1}得意なはずだと
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.04,0:22:27.23,oped,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,400)\be1}振りかえる日々　あぁ
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.68,0:22:33.66,oped,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,400)\be1}探していた　きみをひとり
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.87,0:22:40.30,oped,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,400)\be1}もしもいま許されるなら
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.59,0:22:46.99,oped,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,400)\be1}きみのことだけ想うよ
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.15,0:22:54.88,oped,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,400)\be1}忘れたくない悲しみならば
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.34,0:23:02.42,oped,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,400)\be1}ただそれが　それだけが
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.76,0:23:08.62,oped,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,800)\be1}そう  ひとつの願い
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.07,0:21:47.31,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,400)\be1}太過悲傷的眼眸
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.77,0:21:53.98,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,400)\be1}映照出這片天空
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.35,0:22:02.37,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,400)\be1}不知該說什麼好
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.65,0:22:08.22,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,400)\be1}只默默數著星星
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.74,0:22:13.94,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,400)\be1}孤獨的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.32,0:22:20.72,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,400)\be1}早該習慣了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.04,0:22:27.23,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,400)\be1}回首往日
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.68,0:22:33.66,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,400)\be1}我曾獨自將你找尋
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.87,0:22:40.30,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,400)\be1}若此刻能得到允許
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.59,0:22:46.99,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,400)\be1}我願心中只思念著你
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.15,0:22:54.88,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,400)\be1}若不願忘卻這悲傷
